responsejoke.text:
Q: Why did the vampire get fired from the blood bank?
A: He was caught drinking on the job!

Q: What word in the dictionary is spelled incorrectly?
A: Incorrectly!

Q: One good turn...
A: Usually gets most of the blanket.
Where there is a will, there is an Inheritance Tax!
Creditors have much better memories than debtors.
I was trying to daydream, but my mind kept wandering...

If someone has a mid-life crisis while playing hide & seek...
Do they automatically lose because they can't find themselves?

Why do bagpipe players always walk while they play?
Is it to get away from the noise?

It is better to be healthy than wise...
Being sick costs you money, but you can be dumb for free.

I like work, it fascinates me...
I can sit back and look at it for hours...

Where is the place pencils like to go for a vacation?
Pencil - Vania!

Marriage is mind over matter...
If the husband doesn’t mind, it doesn’t matter.

What's a budget?
A 'Budget' is basically a method for going broke methodically.

A penny for your thoughts...
Or $20 to act them out!

Two rules to success in life...
1. Don't tell people everything you know.

Time takes its toll...
So please have exact change!

The trouble with talking too fast...
Is that you might say something you haven't thought of yet!

They say we learn from our mistakes.
That's why I'm deliberately making as many as possible.
Soon I'll be a genius!

Death and taxes are inevitable...
But at least death doesn't get worse every year!

What kind of alien makes the best of friends?
The one that is down to Earth
The real reason 'Man' is the highest form of intelligence... is because Man does the classifying.

I didn't say it was your fault...
I just said I was blaming you.

To steal ideas from one person is plagiarism
To steal from many is research

Knowledge is knowing a tomato is a fruit.
Wisdom is not putting it in a fruit salad.

There comes a time when all people break down and do the unthinkable...
They read the manual!

The 21st century is bit weird...
Instead of MAKING history, everyone wants more to DELETE history!
A whale swims all day, only eats fish, drinks lots of water, but still weighs a lot!

It's not hard to meet expenses...
They're pretty much everywhere.

When I'm finally holding all the right cards...
Everyone wants to play chess!

To err is human.
To forgive is against company policy.

How did the octopus defeat the shark?
He was well armed!

I started out with nothing!
And I still have most of it left.

What did one horse say to the other?
I can't remember your mane, but your pace is familiar!

I wanted to thank everyone for defining the word 'plethora' for me...
It means a whole lot to me!

Teach your kids about taxes...
Eat 30% of their ice cream

Do married people live longer than single people?
Or does it just feel that way?

I'm changing my name to 'Everyday'...
Because that's what the people I owe money to call me.
Why do they call it the Department of Interior when they are in charge of everything outdoors?

Why did the gardener always eat her toast dry?
Because she saw the butter-fly!!

I don't believe in reincarnation...
I didn't believe in it the last time, either.

Where did the kangaroo go to get its eyesight checked?
To a hop-tician!

Did you hear about the guy who survived being struck by lightning?
He was shocked!

Where do fish keep their money?
In the River Banks.

Do you know how long Grandfather Clocks have been around?
Since the beginning of time...

At my age, rolling out of bed in the morning is easy...
Getting up off the floor is another story.

What ten-letter word starts with G-A-S?
Automobile!

What can you break without touching?
Promise.

What do you get if worms ruled the earth?
Global Warming

Everyone has photographic memory!
Difference is some do not have any film

Bacon was definitely the  first-round draft pick in the BLT...
No one’s building a sandwich around lettuce!
